				<div class="container">
					<div class="box">
						<p class="title">1. Introduction and Acceptance of Terms</p>
						<p class="word">At the beginning of the terms of service, there should be an introduction, stating that users must accept and adhere to these terms. User use of the forum represents their agreement to comply with these regulations.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="box">
						<p class="title">2. User Responsibilities</p>
						<p class="word">Clearly list the user's responsibilities on the forum, including not posting infringing, obscene, offensive, or illegal content, and not abusing forum features, etc. Remind users to respect others.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="box">
						<p class="title">3. Intellectual Property</p>
						<p class="word">Explain that all content on the forum (posts, comments, images, etc.) belongs to the forum or its creators, and users must not illegally copy, distribute, or modify this content.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="box">
						<p class="title">4. User Accounts</p>
						<p class="word">Explain the process of creating user accounts, password security requirements, and user responsibilities for managing and protecting their accounts.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="box">
						<p class="title">5. Complaints and Copyright Infringement</p>
						<p class="word">Provide a complaint mechanism for users to report violations or copyright infringement, while clearly outlining your handling procedures.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="box">
						<p class="title">6. Termination Rights</p>
						<p class="word">Clearly state your right to terminate or suspend user accounts at any time if they violate the terms of service.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="box">
						<p class="title">7. Disclaimer</p>
						<p class="word">Explain that you do not take responsibility for the accuracy and legality of forum content, as well as for any potential losses that may occur.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="box">
						<p class="title">8. Dispute Resolution</p>
						<p class="word">Explain how you wish to resolve disputes, such as through mediation or arbitration.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="box">
						<p class="title">9. Applicable Law</p>
						<p class="word">Specify that these terms are governed by Malaysian law.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="box">
						<p class="title">10. Modification Rights</p>
						<p class="word">Reserve the right to modify the terms of service and remind users to regularly check for updates to the terms.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="box">
						<p class="title">11. Contact Information</p>
						<p class="word">Provide your contact information so that users can reach out to you.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="box">
						<p class="title">12. Notifications</p>
						<p class="word">Specify the method of notification, such as through email or on-site messaging.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
